title: Threads of Destiny
overview: Both of the Jiang family's daughters are reborn. Jiang Xueying, the eldest daughter of the Jiang family, swaps her marriage with her younger sister Jiang Yu'er. As the prince's wife, Jiang Xueying battles cunning rivals in the household, including Jiang Yu'er. She reforms her reckless husband and joins forces with him to expose a sinister conspiracy.
